flowchart LR
    A[Production Endpoint] --> B[Predictions, Inputs, and Metrics]
    B --> C[SageMaker Model Monitor]
    B --> D[Amazon CloudWatch and Logs]
    B --> E[SageMaker Clarify]
    F[AWS CloudTrail] --> G[Audit Trail]
